headline: How Adobe’s (ADBE) AI Partnership with HUMAIN Could Shape Its Middle East Expansion Strategy
summary: HUMAIN announced a global partnership with Adobe at the U.S.-Saudi Investment Forum to develop culturally relevant generative AI models and AI-powered applications for the Middle Eastern market. This collaboration combines local AI expertise with Adobe’s creative technologies, aiming to deliver authentic Arabic content and enhance Adobe’s regional integration through advanced data center use and product synergies. headline: Shoppers spend billions on Black Friday to snag holiday deals, despite wider economic uncertainty
summary: Despite wider economic uncertainty hovering above this year's holiday season, shoppers turned out in big numbers for Black Friday — spending billions of dollars both in stores and online.  Adobe Analytics, which tracks e-commerce, said U.S. consumers spent a record $11.8 billion online Friday, marking a 9.1% jump from last year.  Consumers also spent a record $6.4 billion online on Thanksgiving Day, per Adobe.
